  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nthis `W5ot96` is a bad peer and we can't dial it for all protocols\r\n\r\nthe first time I see the \"request selection failed\" of peer `W5ot96`\r\n```\r\nDec-12 00:00:01.015 [NETWORK]       ^[[36mverbose^[[39m: Req  error method=ping, encoding=ssz_snappy, client=Unknown, peer=16...W5ot96, requestId=727018 code=REQUEST_ERROR_DIAL_ERROR, error={\"message\":\"protocol selection failed\"}\r\nError: protocol selection failed\r\n```\r\nthe last time of the day\r\n```\r\nDec-12 23:56:43.364 [NETWORK]       ^[[36mverbose^[[39m: Req  error method=status, encoding=ssz_snappy, client=Unknown, peer=16...W5ot96, requestId=1134921 code=REQUEST_ERROR_DIAL_ERROR, error={\"message\":\"protocol selection failed\"}\r\nError: protocol selection failed\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nas we dial this peer quite frequently, we should ban it right after seconds/minutes because `DIAL_ERROR` has lower tolerance so this peer should be banned after 5 errors like this\r\n",
